%% Data Flow Diagram - llama-stack-k8s-operator
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as Operator Controller Manager<br/>redhat-ods-applications
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (CR created/updated)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>Operator: Render manifests via Kustomize<br/>(transformers: namespace, name, fields, NetworkPolicy)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment, Service,<br/>NetworkPolicy, PVC, HPA, PDB, SA, RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resource created/updated
    Operator->>LlamaStack: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LlamaStack-->>Operator: 200 OK (healthy)
    Operator->>LlamaStack: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LlamaStack-->>Operator: Provider info JSON
    Operator->>LlamaStack: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LlamaStack-->>Operator: Version info JSON
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update LlamaStackDistribution status<br/>(health, providers, version, routeURL)

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 2: External Access (exposeRoute=true)

    participant ExtClient as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress Controller<br/>80/443 TCP

    ExtClient->>Ingress: HTTP/HTTPS request<br/>Depends on ingress controller config
    Ingress->>LlamaStack: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LlamaStack-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>ExtClient: Response

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 3: ConfigMap Change Detection

    User->>K8sAPI: Update user ConfigMap
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (ConfigMap changed)
    Operator->>Operator: Compute new config hash
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment annotation<br/>(config hash change triggers rollout)
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Rolling restart with new config
